      "title": "The President goes to the National Hospital to see Jackson",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe went to the Colombo National Hospital to check on the well-being of the veteran artist Mr. Jackson Anthony who is undergoing treatment after an accident.",
        "The President also met and talked with the relatives of Mr. Jackson Anthony and asked the hospital staff to pay special attention to Mr. Jackson Anthony's recovery."
